                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <!-- Project Details Go Here -->
                            <h2>Trademarks</h2>
                            <p class="item-intro text-muted"></p>
                            <img class="img-responsive" src="" alt="">
                            <p>We operate in all stages of the protection of trademarks, including clearance by analyzing the registrability of a particular trademark (in a search), up to the actual application to register a trademark before the PTO.
 
In regards to trademark searches we conduct initial clearance searches, analyze the results and prepare a specific report for each client. We frequently work with multinational companies which also specialize in this type of service worldwide, enabling us to access diverse databases, with the additional more important factor of speeding-up the delivery of results to clients.
 
In respect of registering trademarks before the PTO, our staff and partners have ample capacity and experience, providing advice as to the best form of protection for the intellectual property assets of each client, as well as any subsequent defense that may have to be presented in the administrative sphere before the PTO itself.
Our staff is trained to provide clients not only with the comprehensive yet concise answers, but also to be as quick as possible with that response.
 
We operate both in the domestic and international markets, which means that we advise national and international firms on the protection of their intellectual property in Brazil as well as other countries around the world.</p></p>
                            
                                
