                            <!-- Project Details Go Here -->
                            <h2>Industrial Designs</h2>
                            <p class="item-intro text-muted"></p>
                            <img class="img-responsive" src="" alt="">
                            <p>
We also operate in the guidance and protection of Industrial Designs, not only in Brazil, but abroad. 
 
Industrial Designs more often than not, are Intellectual Property assets which are not fully protected within a company, although in many cases they are an equitable solution for the protection of items that are difficult to quantify.
 
We offer assistance in the whole registration process of an Industrial Design before the PTO from filing up until grant of registration.
 
This assistance extends not only in Brazil, but also abroad. </p></p></p>
                            
                                
