                         <div class="modal-body">
                            <!-- Project Details Go Here -->
                            <h2>Software</h2>
                            <p class="item-intro text-muted"></p>
                            <img class="img-responsive" src="" alt="">
                            <p>In Brazil there is a specific law protecting computer software which outlines the parameters of protection available.
 
This protection is strategic to avoid any type of problems cropping up in the future, whether they are in the area of civil law, company law or even employment law. As such, this is an asset which needs to be very well managed within a company.
 
Accordingly, we provide guidance as to the best protection as well as registering Software in Brazil which is done before the PTO and abroad. .</p></p></p>
                            
                                
